          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Sexual assault is any unwanted touching of a sexual nature. It is a broad definition that covers a wide range of conduct, from an unwanted kiss to a violent sexual attack. The key element is the lack of consent."
